Package: MultivCalibration
Type: Package
Title: Evaluate the Calibration of Multivariate Probabilistic Forecasts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Sam", family = "Allen", email = "sam.allen@unibe.ch", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: Tools to evaluate the calibration of multivariate probabilistic forecasts.
    Several prerank functions are provided that condense the multivariate forecasts and 
    observations to univariate objects, to which univariate checks for calibration can be employed.
License: GPL (>= 2)
